{"tid":1423300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己同身邊嘅人每一日都好大壓力 都好唔開心","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:47:37.000Z","uid":191898,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"adcacd973a4c586f35aee0b896d489a3963e4354","tid":1423300,"uid":191898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:28:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/261185104224300/posts/951551305187673?s=1833018656&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F261185104224300%2Fposts%2F951551305187673%3Fs%3D1833018656%26sfns%3Dmo&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=e7550f40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/261185104224300/posts/951551305187673?s=1833018656&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後覺得個人好無力<br />\n好怕之後越嚟越多人睇唔開做傻事去尋死 <br />\n大家覺得可以點同應該點<br />\n我都睇唔到自己同香港未來嘅路應該點行<br />\n係咪應該一齊焦土一齊攬炒定仲有咩出路。。。"},{"pid":"17a7477324fc432344febf2143d0ae6b032f4881","tid":1423300,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b7d5402d5c5763aee80b896bb377dd5a4132b4b","tid":1423300,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adcacd973a4c586f35aee0b896d489a3963e4354","tid":1423300,"uid":191898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:28:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/261185104224300/posts/951551305187673?s=1833018656&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F261185104224300%2Fposts%2F951551305187673%3Fs%3D1833018656%26sfns%3Dmo&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=e7550f40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/261185104224300/posts/951551305187673?s=1833018656&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後覺得個人好無力<br />\n好怕之後越嚟越多人睇唔開做傻事去尋死 <br />\n大家覺得可以點同應該點<br />\n我都睇唔到自己同香港未來嘅路應該點行<br />\n係咪應該一齊焦土一齊攬炒定仲有咩出路。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=392297c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"}]}